{"tid":1938824,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多代mh,發覺好玩既超大型魔物只得峯山龍","createTime":"2020-03-22T20:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T09:52:57.000Z","uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce55ccebe250ca53e7e312ea7790829031d6e3f","tid":1938824,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T20:21:56.000Z","msg":"老山龍- 刷肚刷到完場，過區浪費時間，城門炮台淪為虛設<br />\n<br />\n老山蟹-比老山龍好，，不需要等過區浪費時間，不過都係刷腳刷到完場，炮台仍為虛設<br />\n<br />\n大海龍-海戰版老山龍，不解釋<br />\n<br />\n熔山龍-前半段打弱點太容易，打爆後不能繼續削血，龍太大，浪費大量時間跑點同爬山，後半段只能搬運工，擊龍船淪為炮台一部份，擊龍槍只能放一次就完場<br />\n<br />\n峯山龍：沙地追擊最有狩獵感，唯一一次任務目的不是防禦要塞，擊龍船和龍身是唯二落腳點，炮台弩箭有輸出效果，但不會如熔山龍成唯一輸出手段，擊龍槍可以用3次，打爆核心後可以持續用削血，以及新武裝大銅鑼，同埋峯山龍可以型棍凌空係獵人頭頂跳過船身<br />\n<br />\n最後比條片大家睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lynCjH-MVxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlynCjH-MVxw&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=4e581d45\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lynCjH-MVxw</a>"},{"pid":"db852f591d2a314afbcce9b295c77b46df59b92d","tid":1938824,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"玩過4g未？"},{"pid":"ca68c34c162e7d81fd7c5ef562b84f0d1c2b7ea1","tid":1938824,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db852f591d2a314afbcce9b295c77b46df59b92d","tid":1938824,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"玩過4g未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T20:27:23.000Z","msg":"你想講蛇精龍?"},{"pid":"9991fc3e8a335a6bd2bb9478eeb0f4244e2c7dd4","tid":1938824,"uid":2910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca68c34c162e7d81fd7c5ef562b84f0d1c2b7ea1","tid":1938824,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db852f591d2a314afbcce9b295c77b46df59b92d","tid":1938824,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T20:25:47.000Z","msg":"玩過4g未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T20:27:23.000Z","msg":"你想講蛇精龍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"